{"tid":1542174,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（行動POST）依家831太子站單嘢，好需要各位巴絲一齊搞大佢！","createTime":"2019-09-04T18:37:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T23:27:40.000Z","uid":137224,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"6639d154078a2c71c8ee5f0547a836350d56d7d6","tid":1542174,"uid":137224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T18:37:29.000Z","msg":"第一，    一次拘捕行動出現左10個紅色傷者（紅色傷者代表有即時生命危險），即係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">差啲出左10條人命</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第二，    封站歷時兩日而原因不明，點解出現咗咁多傷者又唔比人急救嘅情況之餘，仲要再封站兩日？<span style=\"color: red;\">黑警需要出嚟交代</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第三，    出現大量疑似傷者變死者的信息，而無一個可以fact check，我哋唯有做到嘅係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">保住個CCTV記錄</span>！</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我呼籲大家！<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">6/9 八點發起太子站靜坐行動！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">20:15分：開始入場，各自搵位坐<br />\n20:31分：靜坐默哀3分鐘<br />\n呢個默哀係爲香港、爲犧牲左嘅義士、爲黑警無左嘅良心默哀<br />\n20:34分後：就各自爬山，喊口號隨你</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n係等嘅過程如果有人逗你，你就話等緊人，吖唔係，喺等緊個交代<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次行動目的有三個訴求：<br />\n1）    追究警方，在傷者無意識下仍拖行傷者+阻礙救護進行急救（當時急救員懷疑傷者脊椎骨折。要求剪開傷者衣物但遭警員以不能破壞證物為由拒絕，後來被獲淮剪一半。另外急救員要求解開手扣，亦被拒絕<br />\n2）    呼籲傷者或者當時當值的職員透過法律途徑告 黨鐵同黑警，從而可以透過《高等法院條例》第41條或者第42條，強制命令要黨鐵交出831當晚既CCTV，咁先可以保住個CCTV個記錄<br />\n3）    要求黑警封站兩日的理由，以及黨鐵無償配合的原因<br />\n<br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">行動代號：爲香港默哀<br />\nDress code：儘量全黑</span></div></strong><br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲到時見！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20f26f35af9481e5c6958ffb1328c2ca4fc3fc22","tid":1542174,"uid":254028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T18:41:11.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"f2d0fe341466d0b4d10b10bb2f125a4447658d31","tid":1542174,"uid":137224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T18:41:32.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"0527151396b281df794c64ca11da6b0c10601e95","tid":1542174,"uid":137224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T18:41:43.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"f34dd48567c9ca63d93cea2f4c6777f0d4beb5a1","tid":1542174,"uid":138677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T18:42:39.000Z","msg":"推爆你個po！！到時見啦巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港！"},{"pid":"1847ec5bfaace6736d81f630e7dbae9802379e10","tid":1542174,"uid":318271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T18:42:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"284f93b9d7046dbd402d01fa3ab3ac1fb71d8f69","tid":1542174,"uid":197121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T18:44:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a9fb4515a39d8f0b4537433ae864e70f263dd5cd","tid":1542174,"uid":137224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T18:44:33.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"a98e3963e798b46db05a1b90fb5e85dc80254da3","tid":1542174,"uid":114121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T18:44:49.000Z","msg":"平反831<br />\n<br />\n請以下人士交代，不論係現身說法或匿名都好<br />\n1. 黨鐵CCTV<br />\n2. CMC / PMH 醫護<br />\n3. 在場消防 / 救護員<br />\n4. 在場黨鐵職員<br />\n4. 其餘當日在場既人見到乜都好，每人將自己所見到既野講出黎，砌返個真相"},{"pid":"6fbe8897aa5b63b5c237c852706265ecb951db63","tid":1542174,"uid":137224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T18:46:57.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"3a4c6af6ef0094fc29c366c2f6a40ab08707cdd8","tid":1542174,"uid":15409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T18:47:55.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfec159fe27e6e31d167c16f4fdf7b4b074253a7","tid":1542174,"uid":138677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T18:48:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25114e2c7e20df0d9126201ac6fba13b58b9875d","tid":1542174,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T18:50:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62d5e6d50c3326f4b10542982260f6100c8b4971","tid":1542174,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T18:50:44.000Z","msg":"平反831"},{"pid":"52b827b1181d1a6060a2d846dfb8063f6f961d89","tid":1542174,"uid":257834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T18:50:55.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fa2db62f6adfc5ba3d85355f41aefa6d4750fbf","tid":1542174,"uid":20908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T18:51:42.000Z","msg":"推！！！！！！！！！！！！！"},{"pid":"4bc04416a44e9566533e29a557a0d5d791dd3a4a","tid":1542174,"uid":138677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T19:01:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"96fab3db89108104acc85d4b4e5f0a31392352a7","tid":1542174,"uid":138677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime