9-09-04T19:13:11.000Z","msg":"平反831"},{"pid":"2c53ab80de9c85d8a44683ae3944861af87cc89c","tid":1542174,"uid":211578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T19:13:25.000Z","msg":"6月9撤回同9月4撤回分別係邊呀?<br />\n分別在於：<br />\n<br />\n殉港手足：<br />\n熊家俊先生（25歲） - 15/12/2017<br />\n梁凌杰先生（35歲） - 15/6/2019<br />\n盧曉欣小姐（21歲） - 30/6/2019<br />\nZhita Wu（29歲） - 30/6/2019<br />\n麥小姐（28歲） - 3/7/2019<br />\n梅先生（32歲） - 5/7/2019<br />\n范先生（26歲） - 22/7/2019<br />\nCalvin 郭先生（25歲） - 27/8/2019<br />\n姬先生（16歲） - 2/9/2019 <br />\n粉嶺女生 - 4/9/2019<br />\n9人離世<br />\n<br />\n還有：<br />\n3隻眼<br />\n2次地鐵恐襲<br />\n2人被刀手斬至重傷<br />\n超過100人被檢控<br />\n超過1000人被捕<br />\n受傷, 逃亡不計其數<br />\n<br />\n淨係計以上的分別, 已經好明顯。<br />\n還有整個警隊及制度的不公義已暴露。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OkC3deC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOkC3deC.jpg&h=34367fd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D2LPVhj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD2LPVhj.jpg&h=35c3dac3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C4TBAhk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC4TBAhk.jpg&h=05bdd3d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t8LoZ1q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft8LoZ1q.jpg&h=fac47d55&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"52f586008a3c134310e1477594720b17df1b28be","tid":1542174,"uid":64012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T19:16:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e7f0b15cb22ddcea6cb0868f0efd0e42d1bd2f34","tid":1542174,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T19:16:42.000Z","msg":"「而無一個可以fact check，我哋唯有做到嘅係保住個CCTV記錄！」<br />\n<br />\n呢樣係我地最無能為力既地方<br />\n<br />\n你估港鐵會聽黑警話定聽市民話？"},{"pid":"1a181327c3df79c7690076f827f7b57045b7d2b5","tid":1542174,"u